Package life.genny.qwandaq.entity

Class BaseEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • life.genny.qwandaq.CoreEntity
      • life.genny.qwandaq.CodedEntity
        • life.genny.qwandaq.entity.BaseEntity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CoreEntityInterface, Serializable, Comparable<Object>, CreatedIntf, BaseEntityIntf
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SearchEntity
    @Entity
public class BaseEntity
extends CodedEntity
implements BaseEntityIntf
    BaseEntity represents a base entity that contains many attributes. It is the base parent for many Qwanda classes and serves to establish Hibernate compatibility and datetime stamping. BaseEntity objects may be scored against each other. BaseEntity objects may not have a deterministic code Examples of derivative entities may be Person, Company, Event, Product, TradeService.
